column5: MEET UP WITH SKEETER FOR THE FIRST TIME TODAY. WAS A VERY CHILLY START AT 6:30. HUNG AROUND AND TRIED AD TRIED TILL 11 AND NOTHIN . NOT EVEN A SNAG. WATER WAS PRETTY DIRTY TO MY SURPRISE SO THAT PLAYED A BIG ROLE. THOUGH WE DID SHARE SOME STORIES AND HAD A FEW LAUGHS AND SOMETIMES ITS NOT ALWAYS ABOUT CATCHIN FISH. TX FOR A GREAT OUTING BRO. CANT SAY WE DIDNT COVER LOTS OF WATER.WE TRIED. TILL NEXT TIME
See Dann, I told you it's not me...
I think your caps lock key is broken.
Nope! That's just the way he types (here and on all sites)! Get with tha program!
Maybe so, but it's terribly annoying!
Thankfully the Caps Lock will have an end... Thank you Google!  http://www.gizmodo.com.au/2010/12/google-wants-to-take-your-caps-lock-away/

add it to the bothered me post.

Mrs K is going to LOL if she reads that!  Oh so    you are Joey...
i agree, cap locks are very annoying.  sorrry u didnt catch fish

Dan... its not me either But then again, my first Steelheading on the river was with CC. I didn't catch anything but a cold, Scott was putting a show! When I left around noon, later he told me he was slamming them when I was gone.  Don't worry about the caps, at my work place, the manager tells us to do any reports and written down notes in capital letters. I think its neat and easier to read.  I'll try to get up Friday morning for some steelheading, may the force be with me.

Disappointing Day, not really. i got to go out fishing. made a new friend. found a new fishing spot(with no fish in it)LOL  with every situation i try to find the positive side & figure out what i can do about it. after long and hard thinking i have come up with mission for me. so far i have RUINED the reputation of GBW,Yonge_one & Canadian copper, as the go to steel head fishermen. my hit list is growing, but i need more victim's to help me complete my mission. LOL  Solopaddler, want to go fishing???????  how about joey, but YOU should wear a float suit
Pretty sure Copper has explained before that he uses caps locks because of an issue with his eye sight.  Its not to be annoying.
I find it rather exciting. Akin to reading a ransom note, eh?
LOL!!!!  I didn't know I had a reputation
if after the G2G you didnt, well you do now geoff...
